{"text": "What is wolfenstein 3d? Its a classic game that was relised in 1992. And still one of mine favorite game of all time. I mean this game started the FPS genre. And even though this game is 23 years old its still fun to play.  So you are playing as William B.J Blazkowicz and you start in a castle wolfenstein which is a prison. You are trying to fight your way out of the prison and. Which can be difficult sometimes. There are many different levels and many different bosses for each episode.  I reccomend this game to every one who loves 90s, retro or FPS games. Killing Hitler in the 3rd episode is allways fun :)", "appid": "2270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063187741", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434628800.0}
