{"text": "This tactical shooter thats okay for all fans of shooters. In the game you have the consistency and competence of warfare, ie such a chaotic shoots in Call of Duty not here. Each opposing side has its own weapons and equipment, as well as each soldier has its own equipment. So you can feel the very global scale of the war and become part of mates of fifty people. And your main task is not just to reshoot all the enemies, and to carry out a point special operation. The game has a great physical game engine with bullet ricochets and various other nuances. So if you like not just corny run and shoot, and still want to think through the course of special operations, do not hesitate and buy this game.", "appid": "393380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198192702526", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1518523200.0}
