{"text": "Well, some Points, the Game Developer must fix! 1.) When you dig underground, you see sometimes the NOWHERE means gap and holes in the Graphic appear! 2.) Sometimes if you Dig, your Player starts to jump on that Spot and you cant move forward nor back or left or right, you stuck and that sucks. 3.) Water could be better, cause if you dig in Water, the Water Surface do not close coorrectly, looks later like you have a hole in the Ocean or a Lake! 4.) Some more Maps would be cool and awesome, with more bigger Citys, Skyscrapers welcome, Police Station also would be welcome or a big Jail, not everything like in an small Village in Texas, where Population is 250 LOL! 5.) The Roads are fine, until you see some Road looking like a Nuclear Bomb was throwed in or some Earthquake happened, we have Vehicles, so how shall we drive, when some Roads are only a Disaster!?! 6.) The Terrain is always near Mountains stupid made, it looks like you run the Moon, Crater after Crater, we play a Human Char not Kangoroos, na! At the End, yea the Game is addictive and makes lot of Fun, Building is cool, only missing some Terrain Flatening Tool, cause i hate domed Terrain, would be cool, if we get some Tool, so we can bulldoze some Spot, we want to build on! Thx game Developer, maybe you can give us some new Pieces, Tools, etc. Tysm, love the Game very much.", "appid": "251570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032814459", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1581249600.0}
