{"text": "As a woman, I wanted to make a comment here and say that this game is exactly what I was looking for. I've never played this type of game before, this was my first venture into \"mature\" games and now that I've played it, I'm afraid that nothing else will live up to it! This game was totally fun and satisfying in terms of drama, scandal, different types of people/personalities, it was oh so dirty, exciting, and sometimes with a bit of taboo thrown in there (which I love.) It touched upon many fantasies of my own. It took me 19 hours to play through this game, and in about 3 days, because I couldn't stop playing. When it ended, I was so bummed! I love this game style, I love Dr. Pink Cake's work, and I hope they continue producing similar style games, because I will be buying them. On a side note, one thing that did bother me was that the female genitalia wasn't always accurate, which definitely took away from it a little. You know how in animated porn, the vagina will be in the middle of the lips, with the lips \"around\" the penis? During sex scenes, it often looked like this, and I would love to see this improved upon in future games. I've bought Acting Lessons and will be playing this next!", "appid": "1126320", "steamid": "profiles/76561199044375102", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "181", "votes_funny": "38", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586692800.0}
