{"text": "Hello Internet :D welcome to review let's get on shall we?  THE ELDER SCROLLS V: SKYRIM ----------------------------------- Summary: SKYRIM! Yes i know i'm three years late from this game, but that doesnt stop me from enjoy this wonderful game. Skyrim made by Bethesda and is a Open-world RPG game. It is by far one of the greatest games i have ever played, this game when i first started to play it granted me vision for the first time 0-0... generally its a great game and we're gonna go on to the gameplay now. Gameplay: Gameplay wise this game is not bad although with the occasional glitches here and there its pretty solid. Horses can defy the laws of physics so let that be a reminder to you.For the field of view you can choose to play in FPS OR TPS. Combat has repetitive cycles and has a pretty sharp weopen sound which iritated me so i actually went and gotten a mod to fix that, like all modders of Skyrim. Graphically: The game provided a good use of textures for back in 2012 even now in 2015 the graphics still holds and is not too bad. However with MODS , THIS GAME CAN BE TURNT TO ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ MAJESTIC ASS UNICORN-FARTING SPRINKLE EATING MASTERPIECE!!! With the right ENB, floral mods, and texture mods. Everything would provide a good aestheic eye-candy. Story:  You are on your way to Helgen, with three other men one named Ralof a soldier for the Stormcloak faction , a generic horse-thief from Rorikstead and the might true High King,Ulfric Stormcloak. Just when you were about to get decaptitated, Alduin, the great black dragon came to Helgen and ♥♥♥♥♥♥ the party up. In the end, you escape to Riverwood with either Harvar or Ralof. One of the either will instruct you to go to Whiterun and inform the Jarl of the situation and it is  there where he sends you to fight a dragon and you discover you are DRAGONBORN! HUZZAH! Final Verdict: THIS GAME I CAN'T STRESS ENOUGH IS A MASTERPIECE !! The modding community is great but that doesnt mean u need it to provide a wonderful time with this game. Gameplay is non-Linear and is what makes SKYRIM great you will be filled with ENDLESS MISC. quests and side quests and discover new lands and become the champions of many Daedric princes. I love this game alot and i would be honored to give this game a 10/10!!! Game is near flawless and i believe the game is worth the price even at full. Thanks so much for reading this review and i hope this has convinced you to purchase the game as im sure you will enjoy it as much as i did .!!!", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075247312", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1443787200.0}
