{"text": "Ok for the ones that say that this is a Pay to Wins game, guys ... you are playing this game FOR FREE. Aside the 2 already unlocked characters which are played on professional matches and can be monsters to play againts ( Aura and Skyhammer ) you are getting 3 free heroes ( mercenaries ) everyweek on rotation.  Yes I am in defense of the game. I have not given a single euro for the game and I love it as it is, remember the free way is slower, but decent.  And ofcourse just like any other game it is better with friends even if you play againts each other. Again don't forget this is a FREE to play game. Aside from that  -  quick dynamic gameplay  - very agile characters ( literally those sick wall jumps )  - abilities do play a huge role, but I would say it is the classes that make the difference - plenty of personas to choose from Now time to break one myth, BRONZE CARDS and COBALT CARDS are te same, the only difference is the skin your character has, I have literally a cobalt card with the same stats as a gold one, same for silver and gold. A side note - cards provide passive buffs like faster reload, 10% more Area of effect range, more ammo clips, faster melee speed. Bronze is all you need, unless you want to show off :P If you want to play as every character either invest time or money, that's it. But once you master a character .... oh boy :) Alot of the characters ( usually per class ) share the same weapons, but you need to craft cards or unlock boxes to get them, don't worry there are certain cards that fit alot of playstyles. A free game after all. I am not saying just because it's free it is free cons and shouldn't be criticized, but again .. a free game this is.", "appid": "333930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091658638", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554033600.0}
