{"text": "I must say my first impression of this game is that I am really impressed, that there is so much to do and the humor is totally my thing! Its fun to play with friends and you always have a challange here and there so it wont get boring. Yes there are repetitive quests or rather tasks and you need to repeat a lot of things like killing enemies in a certain area if you need to track back to places you already visited because a quest told you to do so, but thats fine by me. It is fun to find new weapons to find new equipment and all sorts of stuff and there is always something new to uncover! The character lines are pure gold and I cant belive they are working on Borderlands 3! I cant wait after playing this one and the other 2 Games I own from this series! If you like a game where you can basicly level up infinite amount of times and replay everything when youre done then this game is for you, also dont forget to prepare for a whole bunch of bad jokes and funny refereces because this game has got a bunch of them! (even though I havent played it for that long I already would say the Borderlands Series is one of my favorite and I regret that I havent played the games earlier..) This game gets a rating of 9/10 (because I cant wait for Borderlands 3  :P )", "appid": "261640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118139459", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522843200.0}
