{"text": "If you like killing Nazis this is the game for you.  The first few hours of this game had very much action with a feeling of being badass as you duel wield machine guns and slaughter nazis and half robot german shepards. After that however the game kinda of slows down. When back at base you become an erranad boy because people tell you do certain things for them in order to progress through the story. I really disliked this because i bought the game to kill some ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ NAZIS. Once you get through that part the action starts to pick up again. The mission when you are in space has great atmosphere. You can choose the way you wanna play. if you wanna go stealth then you can. If you wanna go in guns blazing (Which i think makes the game more fun) then go right ahead. i really enjoyed the story and what the main characters stood for. basically Germany won the war and they now rule the world. Obvisouly the main character (you) dosent like that. So you start a group of resistance fighters in order to destory germanys rule across the globe. 8/10 i definetly recommend.", "appid": "201810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198202012453", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1500465600.0}
