{"text": "Turn-based tactical shootout game with steampunk space theme. Gameplay is similar to Worms. PROS: - Interesting lore: world dominated by electic and diesel robots, where old-timey steam-powered robots are becoming obsolete. - Nice cartoon graphics with very smooth animation. - Pleasant soundtrack. - Great tactical gameplay. - Choice of characters with distinct skills and equipment makes for multiple possibilities of level completion. - You never knew that, but you will enjoy shooting and collecting hats. - There are space pirates, robot cowboys and robot cowboy space pirates. - It's possible to play it in 20-40 minute bursts if you are time deficient. MEH: - The levels are procedurally generated. It gives potential for replayability, but also means that sometimes you get a level that is too easy and sometimes you get one that is almost impossible to win. CONS: - none The verdict: great game, very simple to learn and fun to play. GAMEPLAY 10/10 GRAPHICS 9/10 AUDIO 9/10 STORY 8/10", "appid": "322190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198257815585", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539000000.0}
