{"text": "Wizard101 is a game that is actually pretty good in it's own respect. Having logged at LEAST a thousand hours across several accounts and BOTH games, it's definitely not a bad game. Sure, it gets stale at times but breaks are necessary to fully enjoy the game. Maybe space your lengthy playthroughs to every few days. BUT - this game is marketed as free to play, and, well, yeah, it's free to PLAY, but you gotta shell out 10 bucks for a month of everything, or more if you want crowns. Heads up, membership is a better offer, since it lets you do basically everything for however long you decide to pay for. You never really need to make another purchase outside that monthly membership unless you REALLY feel like it. You can easily farm for premium items in some early areas, but they become more available much later into the game. Plus, if you decide you've had enough, even for until the next major update, just cancel any time, as you do. Now, do I recommend this game? Oh, absolutely. If you don't know if you'd like it, just try up until the free trial ends, then decide if it's worth the ten. However, if you already have an account, don't make a new account just to play on Steam for the time being, unless you perhaps don't mind starting over, or even just don't remember the mechanics. You'll be starting from scratch if you do, so it's up to you to make that choice for yourself. Overall, give the game a shot! The storyline is decent and definitely gets better as you go along, should you play far enough at least. :^)", "appid": "799960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198203010513", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1536408000.0}
{"text": "Call of Juarez: The Cartel - Ne příliš úspěšný díl ze série Call of Juarez, příběh se odehrává v současnosti a nechybí zde i místa z předchozích dílů a to konkrétně pevnost Juareze Mendozy. Jednou z hlavních postav je policista Ben McCalla, který je posledním potomkem Billyho Mendozy z prvního dílu. Na rozdíl od ostatních dílů v tomhle chybí duely, ale můžete si vybrat konec příběhu. Call of Juarez: Gunslinger - Příběhově hra nesedí do předchozích dílů, ale o minulých postavách jsou tu zmíňky, hlavní hrdina je jeden takže nehrajete za více postav. Příběh se odehrává ve vyprávění hlavního hrdiny Silase Greavese (jelikož je to příběh tak se v průběhu hraní mění nebo opakuje) plný násilí a nelítostných psanců prérie. Úžasná hratelnost a parádní příběh kde nechybí duely a útržky o pravdivých informacích o postavách ze hry, a jak tomu bylo i předchozím díle můžete si vybrat konec příběhu.", "appid": "204450", "steamid": "profiles/76561198115300086", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588075200.0}
