{"text": "The Yellow Turbans are one of my favorite factions. If you are into the Romance of Three Kingdoms lore, you already know they were a taoist uprising against the corrupt Han dynasty. They are portrayed as villains in the book and most media, but now you can rewrite their role in China's history. You have a bunch of cheap rebel peasants units and some elite fanatical units, including some that rise the moral of the rest of the troops. So ff you are into guerrilla warfare or peasants armies, this is the DLC for you. This DLC was a giveaway if you prepurchased TW:TK As always, thanks Feral Interactive for bringing the Total War franchise to Linux.", "appid": "853360", "steamid": "profiles/76561197987292682", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603627200.0}
