{"text": "As this bring my first review I will express my opinion to my highest extent. CS:GO is my favorite Shooter ive ever experienced. After almost 500 hours of playing it I can now say that ive experienced my highs and lows of this game but overall I always find enjoyment in this game. It is so entertaining and is such a excellent way to kill time. Valve has always tried to make this game better and better each patch/update (Referring to the bot nuke).  CSGO has some of the most intriguing attributes I have ever seen in any other shooters I have experienced. This game actually has a spray pattern, the grenades throws, the fact how your aim is off when you run ect... The price of this shooter is a steal. $15 for a game that does not bull$%!# you and make you purchase map packs/expansions that will empty your wallet. When you purchase CSGO, you're getting the WHOLE game! The only thing about this game that is degrading to the community is the hacking in the community and pro community. But hacking is inevitable in any game. But, unlike any other game, Valve lets the community download and review the reported players past \"demos\" and judge/vote if they have been using hacks ect..  Overall this game is an all around fun shooter that will lead you coming back for more even after you lose a competitive match. It is easy to jump into and user friendly for all! Id suggest you give it a try!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026985419", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1432641600.0}
