{"text": "This game has had a great positive impact on my life as someone with rather extreme social anxiety due to physical and mental ailments and I would strongly suggest playing this game if you're in a similar situation and desire some socialisation. The game has a fantastic community with some truly unique personalities on it, I've made a lot of great friends on this game and made a lot of great and hilarious memories. The people in this game gave me a lot of self confidence in socialising, in my singing, playing my guitar and ukulele and dancing which has converted into real life confidence. If you asked me if I wanted to get drunk and do karoake with 5-20 random people before I spent time with the people in this game I would have dug a hole into the ground to escape but now it's just ...easy. The game also encouraged me to get a full VR set-up to show off some dancing and to return the headpats people so graciously gave me when I first joined. :P This game is truly a fantastic and unique gaming experience and I recommend everyone try it, even without a VR set up.", "appid": "438100", "steamid": "profiles/76561197986293674", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1584964800.0}
