{"text": "Let me start off with stating that having regular and social anxiety is absolutely horrible.  If there was a ever a game that could depict my daily struggles with this issue, then this little masterpiece covered it wonderfully.  The constant struggle to be able to complete some basic interactions with other human beings can be be the most excruciating task to do if you are someone that deals with anxiety.  This game covers pretty much what most of us deal with on a day to day basis. I adore the fact that it even touches on the fact  . I know most of us are here for the easy achievements, but try to enjoy the storyline as well, if anything, it will either appeal to you as you share similar feelings described in the story or at least give you an insight and maybe help you understand how those dealing with anxiety feel.", "appid": "792030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198097617064", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546084800.0}
