{"text": "One of my absolute favourite games of all time! This is some of the best money I've ever spent on a game. I have bought it for every console I can so I can play it whenever - 3DS, Switch, PC, Xbox, you name it! It is the best rogue-like game that you will ever play with a replay value that curb stomps any other game. I have 300%'d this game on PC (3 save files 100%) and surpassed 100% on others. The game does an amazing job at constantly rewarding you and wanting you to play again and again. The storyline is absolutely amazing and the bosses never stop getting better and better. Furthermore, the seemingly endless items that you always have more of to unlock make for unique and interesting runs every single time. It is one of those games you can just play for hours and hours on end, take breaks from, and always feel like you can pick up right from where you left off. The game also has a great community surrounding it that builds thousands of beautiful free mods for you to use if you ever feel the need to spice up the game (an urge that should only develop after a few hundred hours). If you like rogue-like games at all, or hell, just have 15 bucks to spare, there is no good reason for you to not pickup this gem.", "appid": "250900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010500057", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "56", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599480000.0}
