{"text": "The remake of the second version of the game, which was released in 2019, was really great and was able to revive the spirit of horror and survival of old titles for us. But when you get to the third version, you really regret it and when you realize that making this title at the same time as the second version It's started, again why do you regret it more? At the beginning of the game, it promises a good title. When you encounter the famous monster in the first scene, the feeling of hatred for the game comes alive in you and you no longer have the energy to continue the game. A garbage bag is placed on Nemesis. You shoot him, this garbage bag goes away, how did they really manage to do this with this myth? The intricacies and scary bosses are all forgotten. Clock tower stage, park stage, giant worm bass. Yes, this is what we are facing in the reconstruction of this title, and the monster itself is the worst, it comes in some predicted places. And there is practically no fear or apprehension for you while he has to play the main role. The story of the game has changed and is not faithful to the original version. Nikolai's character is less present and its characterization is practically weaker. Even the stages that There are shorter in the game. The fights in the game are good and there are different weapons in the game and their variety is also good. Lee's game is so short that not all of them can be used. The enemies of the game are not interesting and do not have a good design, as well as variety. Unfortunately, we are not faced with an interesting title, and after you finish the game once, there is no motivation for a second time, even with the opening of the game store called Point Shop. Good luck. بازسازی نسخه دوم بازی که در سال ۲۰۱۹ منتشر شد واقعا فوق العاده بود و توانست روح وحشت و بقا عناوین قدیمی رو برای ما زنده کنه.ولی وقتی به نسخه سوم میرسید،واقعا تاسف میخورید و وقتی باز میفهمید که ساخت این عنوان همزمان با نسخه دوم آغاز شده است،باز بیشتر افسوس م