{"text": "Honestly, this game is embarrassing. Absolute waste of time, where you get punished for being a noob, don't get taught how to not be one, and is the most sparse, unintuitive pile of steaming garbage known to game design. The absurd rate at which food and hydration decrease, the utter lack of any decent weapon or clothing spawns that haven't already been picked clean due to the ridiculously low spawn times and the bland map (and the brand new one shiny sparkly one which is just a rehash of a different games map copy-pasted) all serve to create the first, and worst purchase I have ever made on steam. I tried to love it, I really did, but in the 6 or so years since buying this, it has only given me reason to not. Do not buy this game. You won't have fun. I fell for the meme of buying this game, let's just hope you don't too.", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198161238664", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588507200.0}
